            <description><![CDATA[【搬砖人脱发有救！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8E%8B%E5%8A%9B%E5%A4%A7%E8%84%B1%E5%8F%91%E8%83%BD%E5%86%8D%E9%95%BF%E5%9B%9E%E6%9D%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8E%8B%E5%8A%9B%E5%A4%A7%E8%84%B1%E5%8F%91%E8%83%BD%E5%86%8D%E9%95%BF%E5%9B%9E%E6%9D%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#压力大脱发能再长回来#</span></a>】医生表示，因紧张、焦虑、睡眠不足等引起的脱发多属于休止期脱发，不会破坏毛囊，有救<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>！通过调节身心状态，对症治疗，三个月到半年，头发就会再长出来。女性产后脱发也可以恢复，新手妈妈们保持良好心态，吃好喝好睡好，不必过度担忧。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[酷]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_ku-774d16f5ce.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（央视网） <a href="http://t.cn/A6jUujZv" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
